<head>MOTHER-IN-LAW</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">岳母</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>MOTHER of HUSBAND OR WIFE.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for a mother-in-law is gū 姑, and this concept was of great importance in ritual practice.</p>
        </div>
